org.apache.distributedlog.namespace

Class DistributedLogNamespaceBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.distributedlog.namespace.DistributedLogNamespaceBuilder

  • public class DistributedLogNamespaceBuilder
extends Object
    Builder to construct a DistributedLogNamespace. The builder takes the responsibility of loading backend according to the uri.
    Since:
    0.3.32
    See Also:
    DistributedLogNamespace
